    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新大陆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精心制作的地图，此地图包含互相独立的玩家对战区域和人机对战区域，让人人都能找到适合自己的内容。在特殊的综合对战区域，你可以狩猎危险的野人，获取珍贵资源。请时刻保持警惕，如果其他玩家也在争夺一样的宝藏，你就可能成为被猎杀的对象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/9e9513cb63e85a058b0347e3b25bcd94.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/9e9513cb63e85a058b0347e3b25bcd94.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/9e9513cb63e85a058b0347e3b25bcd94.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>优化制作与建造</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源并锻造高质量的武器和装备。配方经过简化更加清晰，使你能够把更多时间投入游戏的其他重要方面。你可以建造简陋的庇护所，也可以打造繁荣的村庄乃至坚不可摧的城堡，想造什么就造什么。唯一能限制你发挥才能的就是想象力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/19c3af9b85df755bc009a5465d69ba43.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/19c3af9b85df755bc009a5465d69ba43.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/19c3af9b85df755bc009a5465d69ba43.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态角色成长</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要多个角色来担任不同职务的日子已经一去不复返了。在《Life is Feudal: Arden》中，你可以随时通过前往附近的私人或盟友领地石来切换主要角色的战斗技能。想把双手剑换成弓或矛？轻轻松松就能搞定，你可以根据需要随时调整！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/8f3d203415adb2db386d5989473889ae.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/8f3d203415adb2db386d5989473889ae.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/8f3d203415adb2db386d5989473889ae.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>写实的交易系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Life is Feudal: Arden》中，交易系统几乎与现实无异。交易站点数量有限，你必须谨慎选择站点位置。货物不能即时送达。你得亲自运送待售的货物。而且要小心——沿途有强盗埋伏，随时可能袭击你的商队。不管你打算保卫货物还是想当个强盗，都要时刻留意通商路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/bbd1adefeeb05019fece14c4fa4c3a06.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/bbd1adefeeb05019fece14c4fa4c3a06.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/bbd1adefeeb05019fece14c4fa4c3a06.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特又带有史诗风格的战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Life is Feudal: Arden》中的战斗既直观又真实——打击敌人需要精准的操作，身体属性也至关重要。你可以与盟友并肩作战，参与大规模战斗或攻城战，也可以在竞技场中通过玩家之间的单人对战或团战磨练自己的技艺。战场就是你的游乐场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5686a2f584ac0ec1fe902e24c6c8a18c.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5686a2f584ac0ec1fe902e24c6c8a18c.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5686a2f584ac0ec1fe902e24c6c8a18c.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>权力斗争和政治阴谋</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入真实的政治沙盒中，在这里大家可以组成联盟，又可能反目成仇。参加大规模攻城战和领土战争，征服写实的世界地图上的土地，向败者征税。这是个成王败寇的世界，只有胜者才有资格书写历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5eb73202e8831889abfb282ec95b2a46.poster.avif?t=1772010799\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5eb73202e8831889abfb282ec95b2a46.webm?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285700/extras/5eb73202e8831889abfb282ec95b2a46.mp4?t=1772010799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创造你自己的中世纪王国</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入一个真实又充满无限可能的中世纪世界，你在这里的每一个决定不仅会影响游戏体验，还会改变游戏本身的发展。《Life is Feudal: Arden》是与玩家紧密合作开发的，玩家的反馈推动了许多重要选择。你的意见会直接影响游戏的未来发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
